Package: kitesquare
Title: Vizualize Contingency Tables Using Kite-Square Plots
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("John", "WiedenhÃ¶ft", , "john.wiedenhoeft@medizin.uni-leipzig.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6935-1517"))
Description: Creates a kite-square plot for contingency tables, using ggplot2. It displays all its relevant quantities (marginal, conditional, expected, observed, chi-squared) in an intuitive plot, which resembles a flying kite inside a square if the variables are independent, and deviates from this the more dependence exists.
